longBusinessSummary: Bafna Pharmaceuticals Limited manufactures and sells finished pharmaceutical formulations in India. It also exports its products to Europe, the United Kingdom, Australia, Sri Lanka, Africa, and internationally. The company was founded in 1981 and is based in Chennai, India. Bafna Pharmaceuticals Limited operates as a subsidiary of SRJR Lifesciences LLP.
